Bluetooth doesnt seem to work after install on my EEEpc 1215. Any suggestions.

@Capsin. Had the same issue, couldn't detect BT mouse. Found that Bluetooth Support Service was inactivated. Go to Run, type services.msc, hit enter, find above service, start it and set it to automatic, done. Finding/adding BT devices should now work.
